            <h2 id="Knowing Your Rights">Knowing Your Rights</h2>
            <p>A new European Union law, called General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), gives specific rights to internet users in relation to their personal data. As available and except as limited under applicable law, the rights afforded to users are:</p>
