                <li><span style="color: #f19106">Right to Erasure</span>: the right to request that we delete your personal data.</li>
                <li><span style="color: #f19106">Right to Restrict</span>: the right to request that we temporarily or permanently stop processing all or some of your personal data.</li>
                <li><span style="color: #f19106">Right to Object</span>:
